  notes: >
    Experimental data collected at the University of Arizona Radiation Imaging Laboratory.
    Reference acquisition scripts and detector characterization provided by Max Teicheira
    (University of Arizona). RENA-3 emulation motivated by Yi Gu's CZT PET system
    at Stanford University.
